{"type": "article", "id": 30697, "title": "冰激凌蜡烛", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-07T22:52:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160807201510gqGykxRNCIsMnZQv.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>夏天中甜蜜的烦恼之一或许就是融化得太快的冰激凌了。来自韩国的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kimkimlab/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kim Kim Lab</a> 就突发奇想，为那些变得温暖的冰激凌设计了一系列可爱的表情，巧妙地将这些造型与蜡烛结合在一起，并将这个系列命名为 Do you know the warm ice cream。看着这些“萌化”的冰激凌蜡烛，还真的有些舍不得点燃。目前这个设计还处于原型阶段，尚未开始销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807201534fIaECblY9FtXKuBL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.493888\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807201534XrcmEbJHg4zVuCs5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807201535GPOtNBAe3ilqyEfQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807201537keG2hJWMA8I5631X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}